###
### Supported aliases:
###  core-site:
###     hdfs_namenode_host -> (fs.defaultFS, hdfs://$value:8020)
###
###  hdfs-site:
###     hdfs_namenode_host -> (dfs.namenode.http-address, $value:50070)
